Localization.Name: Cal-O-Meal "Lunes" Protein Bar
Localization.Description:
NDR: 20
Effects: Hypertrophic

Cal-O-Meal bars are loaded with high quality protein and packed with a concentrated dose of vitamins, minerals, and rich Lunes fruit-flavor, making it a convenient way to maintain nutrition and lean muscle mass on the go.
